Source: rf-2a4m1-dkms
Section: kernel
Priority: optional
Maintainer: GenBasic <engineering@genbasic.com>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), dkms
Standards-Version: 4.6.2
Homepage: https://github.com/GenBasic/genbasic-rf-2a4m1

Package: rf-2a4m1-dkms
Architecture: all
Depends: dkms (>= 2.1.0.0), ${misc:Depends}
Recommends: rf-2a4m1-firmware
Description: GenBasic RF-2A4M1 USB Wi-Fi driver (DKMS, GPL source)
 Fully-GPL cfg80211 kernel module for the GenBasic RF-2A4M1 single-band
 2.4 GHz (1T1R) 802.11b/g/n USB Wi-Fi adapter. Compiled from source by DKMS
 against the running and installed kernels, so it rebuilds automatically on
 kernel upgrade. Architecture-independent (no prebuilt object).

Package: rf-2a4m1-firmware
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}
Description: GenBasic RF-2A4M1 on-chip firmware image
 The on-chip firmware image (rf-2a4m1.bin) for the GenBasic RF-2A4M1 adapter,
 plus the driver-binding integration (modprobe/udev). Loaded at runtime by the
 rf-2a4m1 driver. Proprietary; see LICENSE.firmware.
